Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
The property sits adjacent to the new Westar Development, which is anchored by neighborhood retail and the Marriott Renaissance hotel and conference center. 

The property is surrounded by medical offices such as the Westerville Surgery Center, Westerville Close to Home Center, the Westar Urgent Care, Comprehensive Eyecare, and the Center for Surgical Dermatology. 

The area boasts abundant retail and amenities such as the Westerville Recreational Center, Starbucks, Bru Burger, Hot Chicken Takeover, The Winking Lizard, Rusty Bucket and more.
